{"tid":860374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【海傲灣買家】馮生：阿仔用544萬入市「香港樓無得輸」","createTime":"2018-10-13T09:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T14:00:20.000Z","uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f71b4939f309cd608729e46ee3ed94a53a94c0","tid":860374,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"油塘海傲灣跌市開售，居住觀塘的馮先生今日與兒子一齊揀樓，兒子今年27歲從事會計行業，是次斥544萬購入項目一房戶，用以收租投資。他指阿仔好慳家，每個月淨係使3,000元，儲了100多萬元決定自行入市不靠父幹。<br />\n近期樓市下跌，馮生認為：「香港越來越多人，住屋需求不斷有，長遠來講香港樓無得輸。」<br />\n另一名買家陳小姐操流利普通話，持有香港身份證，是次用400多萬元購入項目開放式戶，首期佔一成。入市是因為近期租金好貴，決定買樓自住，亦心儀該盤海景，不過她指買入的單位則沒有海景。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181012/large/1539358091_f565.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181012%2Flarge%2F1539358091_f565.jpg&h=062f8829&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3254a22bef1520179d4564298a0b3f381023865c","tid":860374,"uid":27866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:54:09.000Z","msg":"叻仔，唔洗過多幾年好似連登啲淡友咁，剩係識mon住新聞跌嗰少少就打曬J。"},{"pid":"9cb36e7e9412ef82c1b630d0eb9ff9b657f1f1f8","tid":860374,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"馮生,是我們心中紅太陽"},{"pid":"6db190dc905d173b67d33aa7e2805e7c8252e846","tid":860374,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:58:31.000Z","msg":"轉售為租，<br />\n過完呢一浸，<br />\n樓市又可以繼續gogogo。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51e602fab837a517fb6f71ae75a1e997754d05e","tid":860374,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/om9ViWa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fom9ViWa.gif&h=91f10cbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01f0b58a5d3130633ec44e53caad75fdb5504b0d","tid":860374,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited